{"tid":2267965,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"過了追溯期！南韓華城連續殺人犯 以證人出庭承認殺害14人","createTime":"2020-11-02T12:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T21:59:54.000Z","uid":75656,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"21b0dace2517d72bff4fb1f805e2aeb435202be2","tid":2267965,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:31:18.000Z","msg":"曾高懸30多年未破的南韓華城連環殺人案，由於DNA檢驗技術的進步，去年掌握到兇嫌是因為姦殺小姨子仍然在監獄坐牢的李春在，但華城一案早已過了追溯期，無法追究李春在的罪行。<span class=\"red\">諷刺的是，李春在今（2日）更是以證人的身分而非被告的身分出現在法庭上，承認自己殺害14人。</span><br />\n<br />\n據《韓聯社》報導，李春在今天之所以會出庭，是因為華城連環殺人案的第8起事件，亦即1988年13歲女學生遭姦殺一案。<span class=\"red\">此案雖然是由李春在犯下，但當年警察卻認為這是模仿犯作案，隨即抓捕了無辜的尹姓青年。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">尹男1審被判無期徒刑後百口莫辯，上訴2、3審都被駁回，直到2009年服刑20年後才假釋出獄。</span>因此，在華城連續殺人案真兇李春在坦承自己的犯行後，尹男隨即於去年11月向法院申請冤案重審。<br />\n<br />\n南韓法院今年1月同意重審後，由於檢方和律師都申請李春在以證人身分出庭，<span class=\"red\">法院也接受了雙方的請求，但拒絕媒體在現場拍攝，因為李春在是「證人」而非被告。</span><br />\n<br />\n不過，考慮到外界急於想知道李春在的證詞，法院仍開放了有88個旁聽席的主法庭，在社交距離的原則下可坐44人。從現場狀況可以看到，<span class=\"red\">現年53歲的尹男開庭時坐在被告席上（冤案未推翻之前他仍是被告），一言不發地看著真兇李春在。</span><br />\n<br />\n李春在於法庭上作證，他就是1980年代華城和清州14起連環殺人案的兇手。李春在第1起案件發生於1986年9月，到現在已經34年了，第8起案件則距離現在32年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3339421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3339421&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxRA11HdiY488GD%2FHa51CVEA%3D&h=8682f890\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3339421&h=92285654\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3339421</a>"},{"pid":"5b4966cff56816a6101049dfb92eb28e743771f2","tid":2267965,"uid":165749,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:34:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f137072c960b7df29d7bd9a64f57dd5ca3f5daa7","tid":2267965,"uid":253016,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:35:33.000Z","msg":"CLS 坐足20年<br />\n哭L左"},{"pid":"532c217b99f305a3cac17afbb39d1a512fa7da0b","tid":2267965,"uid":316927,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:35:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾韓警"},{"pid":"ecbd7ea17185fb03831fbf2c480663747de8ff5d","tid":2267965,"uid":144466,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:38:18.000Z","msg":"戇鳩公訴期幾時肯取消"},{"pid":"3dcda0cc45af7045c8160883d09f1b6a96d898ca","tid":2267965,"uid":57513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f137072c960b7df29d7bd9a64f57dd5ca3f5daa7","tid":2267965,"uid":253016,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:35:33.000Z","msg":"CLS 坐足20年<br />\n哭L左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:46:49.000Z","msg":"慘過死"},{"pid":"2316cc20c4538de0bb55beea08078a3072ee7ff2","tid":2267965,"uid":54516,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ecbd7ea17185fb03831fbf2c480663747de8ff5d","tid":2267965,"uid":144466,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:38:18.000Z","msg":"戇鳩公訴期幾時肯取消"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:54:58.000Z","msg":"南韓已經取消自2000年發生嘅殺人事件公訴時效，但係華城連環殺人案發生係2007年前，07年前公訴時效係15年，之後改做25年，2015年再改為直至案件完結。"},{"pid":"9c245fe5d7b8ece9ccf4d1a7360249f3d2f94f08","tid":2267965,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f137072c960b7df29d7bd9a64f57dd5ca3f5daa7","tid":2267965,"uid":253016,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:35:33.000Z","msg":"CLS 坐足20年<br />\n哭L左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T13:17:06.000Z","msg":"兩年都嫌多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7833f21eb22c5d9019d37cbe631bf68f0bfb30e3","tid":2267965,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9c245fe5d7b8ece9ccf4d1a7360249f3d2f94f08","tid":2